Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你快说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, please
