Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All mine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:04:00.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(664.925,160)}情人节嘉年华
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  大家都出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的嘉年华
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my carnival
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物不是嘉年华
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not the carnival
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  要不你就收下这两毛五再
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, why don't you take this quarter and
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, a quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很想要这两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted a quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not the quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快拿着这两毛五去买点棉花糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now take that quarter and buy some cotton candy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棉花糖  我真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy, I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪呼叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪呼叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请回答  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收到珊迪  我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten-four, Sandy, SpongeBob here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已看到嘉年华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a visual on the carnival
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让我把巧克力带进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want me to bring her in?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别进来  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not yet, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星还在猜他情人节礼物是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's still trying to guess what his valentine is
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真会逗人家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are such a kidder
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy out
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个海绵宝宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扇贝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scallops
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃巧克力的扇贝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate-eating scallops
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那如果不是棉花糖的话  会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if it's not cotton candy, then what is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得猜猜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to guess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(801.114,602)}鱼太太算命
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这顶帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This tent
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.22,0:04:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(909.265,198)}旋转爱心
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只草履虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This paramecium?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.40,0:04:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a sly one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之所以我在嘉年华里头找不到礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't find it here in the carnival
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为礼物在爬上去摔下来山顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because it's on top of mount climb-up-and-fall-off
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物也不在那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there, either
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪呼叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把礼物带进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can bring it in now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我这出了点小问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, we've got ourself a little problem
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这有一群吃巧克力的扇贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a pack of chocolate-eating scallops
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要盗走气球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,trying to rustle the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开  爱吃甜食的害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away, you sweet-toothed varmints
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可能会晚一些到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a little late
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.98,0:05:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Late?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.31,0:05:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他带到摩天轮顶端
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take him up to the Ferris wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在那跟你会合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll meet you there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.07,0:05:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是派大星收不到情人节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If Patrick doesn't get his valentine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很确定礼物不在那上面  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's not up there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实是在摩天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually it's on the Ferris
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摩天轮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ferris wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在准备好要收到全世界最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready for the greatest valentine present
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节礼物了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the whole world now, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接收礼物的地方就是这了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is where you're going to get it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直往那看  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just keep looking out there, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请回答  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪呼叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边遇上了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got my ox in a hitch here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,严重偏离航线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm way off course
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扇贝在吃气球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The scallops are eating the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要下坠了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going down, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,执行B计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Switch to Plan B
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要B计划  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No B, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要B计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No B
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知不知道有时计划一样特别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you know how sometimes you plan something special
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果却又事事不顺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and things just don't work out?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy mackerel
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这上边是太热了还是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it hot up here or what?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节礼物  情人节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Valentine, valentine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Valentine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.10,0:07:09.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:09.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Valentine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.36,0:07:09.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:09.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物在这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是握手  亲切友好的握手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A handshake, a friendly handshake
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A handshake?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是盛大礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the big gift?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就送了我一场握手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got me a handshake?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是亲切友好的握手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A friendly handshake
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(747.039,302)}超棒好朋友\N充气城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.972,568)}欢乐屋
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起先一场握手看起来分量并不大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At first a handshake doesn't seem like much
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正重要的是你关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really it's the thought that counts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要谢谢你送我这盒巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you for this box of chocolates
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  弗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, Fran
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  即使我本来一直在期待更多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, even though I was expecting more
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送我玫瑰  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the roses, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's Day
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也一样  戴夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You too, Dave
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并不是说我们当了这么久的朋友如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that it matters that we've been friends for so long
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  谢谢你送我自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, thanks for the bike
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能相信这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you believe this guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早上才刚认识他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just met him this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以如我所说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, as I was saying
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  请问现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, do you guys have the time?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星也需要爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick needs love, too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470.655,878)}气球
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要反抗你  爱心人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I defy you, heart man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一只在逃的粉红胖海星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a chubby pink starfish on the loose
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱心棒必须死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heart on stick must die
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱心棒必须死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heart on stick must die
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把海绵宝宝交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让我心碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You broke my heart
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要弄碎你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm going to break something of yours
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道这是我的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I deserve this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他们也得这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but do they?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们也什么都没给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They didn't give me anything, either
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  现在已经太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's too late for that now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们全都太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for all of you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点走  小贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get along, little shellfish
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快飞  你们这些扇贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giddap, you scallops
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  珊迪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sandy's here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星快看  礼物到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick, it's here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界最棒的情人节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The best valentine in the whole wide world
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在你身后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is right behind you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure it is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说它就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you it's right there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快转身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  转个身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, just turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大笨蛋  快转身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, nincompoop, turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们肯定觉得我很笨是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must think I'm pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快转身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转身  转身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around, turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就再说这么一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say this once
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且这也是最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm not going to say it again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都注意好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so pay attention
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I repeat
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.40,0:11:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会再因为任何原因转过身去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not going to turn around for any reason ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情人节快乐  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's Day, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的情人节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My valentine
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this solid chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没必要什么都给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you didn't have to give me anything
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.02,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(315,308)}纸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.67\pos(242.337,376)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:59.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.67\pos(408.568,700)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.67\pos(422.588,334)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.67\pos(262.365,322)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.67\pos(412.574,638)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该放松了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to relax
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, time to go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你掉了这张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You dropped this piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  所以怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得你可能会想要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just figured you probably want it back
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.94,0:12:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这又有什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.78,0:12:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一垃圾罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Garbage?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果交给正确的人手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the right hands
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这张纸就会成为充满着休闲娱乐的金矿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this paper is a gold mine of entertainment
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一整个精彩下午的海底乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A spectacular afternoon of underwater fun
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充满着财宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A treasure trove of
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you don't want it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.38,0:12:57.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:57.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是表示我可以收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I can have it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, by all means
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快收下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.09,0:13:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再说最后一次  我不要那破纸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the final time, I don't want that paper
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后永远都是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's yours forever and ever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你十分确定以及肯定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So are you definitely, positively sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But are you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一次反悔的机会了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Last chance to change your mind, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你快收下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我收下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it, please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And promise me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.70,0:13:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论我怎么向你求向你要向你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no matter how much I may beg and plead and cry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都别把那纸还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't give that paper back to me ever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以就当这是不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I take that as a possible no?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.34,0:13:40.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:40.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.21,0:13:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么说定了  我只能把纸留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a promise, I'll just have to keep
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  纸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Paper
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.22,0:13:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好幸运能有章鱼哥那样的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so lucky to have a friend like Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底是在笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you giggling about?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.99,0:14:07.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:07.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's just
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just that I'm thinking of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用这张纸的能弄出来的所有玩法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all the fun I'm going to have with this piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会有人能玩一张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can anyone have fun with just a piece of paper?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他用那破纸能玩出什么花样来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can he possibly be doing with that paper?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜猜我是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.06,0:14:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,答对了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是裤子里卡了纸的海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a sponge with paper stuck in his pants
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我还是吸干犯罪的超级海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm also super sponge soaking up crime
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  这是我的斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, here's my cape
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级白痴还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Super moron's more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.70,0:14:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我是丛林宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm SpongeBob JunglePants
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丛林宝宝呼唤动物伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob JunglePants summon animal friends
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是丛林小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not a jungle boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是一箱军需物资
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a box of army supplies
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为饥饿的士兵们带来援助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bringing relief to the hungry troops
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,着陆及时  刚好能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Landing just in time for
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斗牛赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bullfight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toro
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toro, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公牛冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toro, toro
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.41,0:15:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toro
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.95,0:15:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toro
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, ole
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来做滑稽表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for some impressions
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长胡子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a guy with a mustache
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我  我是长胡子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me, I'm a guy with a mustache
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴眼罩的海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pirate with an eye patch
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  我是海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arr, I'm a pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴眼罩的普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A regular guy with an eye patch
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  我不是海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arr, I am not a pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干脆扮个拿着破纸的黄色大白痴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do a big yellow idiot with a stupid piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did he do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嚼纸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oral-gami
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bird
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snowflake
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸片人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paper doll
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那小纸片好像还挺好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That little paper does seem like fun
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am such an idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的  海绵宝宝跟他那张破纸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, honestly, and his dumb paper
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管那叫好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He calls that fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看点无聊科学文摘  这才叫好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now reading boring science digest, that's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1073.493,686)}无聊科学
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看腐蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check erosion
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有丝分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mitosis
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  我连洗澡都玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, I can have fun taking a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画水果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Painting fruit--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画水果最最好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more fun than painting fruit
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比什么都好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is more fun than anything
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要向他证明那张纸一点都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll prove to him that paper is not fun
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm having fun
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棒不棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了海绵宝宝  来超越我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob, top this one
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, little Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西又灰又丑  还长着六条胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's gray and ugly and has six arms?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.08,0:17:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道  可是你照过镜子了没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but have you looked in the mirror lately?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.25,0:17:51.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:51.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.59,0:17:51.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:51.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来让我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听过什么好笑话吗  纸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you heard any good jokes, Mr. Paper?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸掉进海里出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the paper that fell in the ocean?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸掉进海里出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the paper that fell in the ocean?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all washed-up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.57,0:18:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我玩新买的贝壳车玩得好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm having so much fun with my new shell cart
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你的破纸能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, can your stupid paper do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你用一张纸演奏不出音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't play music with a piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.63,0:18:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was great, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吹错的所有音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All those wrong notes you played
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,显得你那曲子更像原创的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,made it sound more original
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没吹错音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't play any wrong notes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  你是这么吹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, you're playing it like this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来一般要这么吹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When ordinarily it goes like this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我个人更偏向用a小调来吹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm partial to doing it in the key of a-minor, myself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友之间的双重奏最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a duet between buddies
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eh, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把纸还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me my paper back
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let go of it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said let go of it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说不行是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you can't?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made me promise
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.05,0:19:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论你怎么向我求向我要向我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no matter how much you begged and pleaded and cried
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都别把那纸还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not to give the paper back to you ever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可没说过那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never said anything like that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说过了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure you did, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你快收下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我收下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it, please
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And promise me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.24,0:19:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论我怎么向你求向你要向你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no matter how much I may beg and plead and cry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.70,0:19:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都别把那纸还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't give that paper back to me ever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要再看一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to see it again?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  我不想再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to see it again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把纸还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just give me that paper
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.79,0:19:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要信守承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sworn to a promise
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should get going
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.00,0:19:56.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:56.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该可以拿东西做交换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe we can trade for something
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.05,0:19:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东西  东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:19:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,something, something
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait up, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.18,0:20:02.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:02.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.88,0:20:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, chum
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你出个价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make you an offer
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口袋漏出来的绒毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pocket lint
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真会讨价还价  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You drive a hard bargain, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿纸换绒毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paper for lint
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是绒毛  是橡皮筋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the lint, the rubber band
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,橡皮筋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rubber band?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该换吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I dare?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dare
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dare
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在考验我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just testing me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会让你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证就是保证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A promise is a promise
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不达成交易你哪都别想去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you are not going anywhere until we strike a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要弄到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to get that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,paper
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.26,0:20:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trade
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有东西都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything must
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我最后的家当了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the last of it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了我穿的衬衣  其他东西都给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've given you everything but the shirt off my back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  这是不是还是考验的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, is this still part of the test
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause it's
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.23,0:21:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信守承诺真的越来越难了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's really getting harder and harder
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep my promise
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, the shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收下  收下我的衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it, take my shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥的衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都好爱那件衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always loved that shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll trade
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会为了这个打破诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can break a promise for this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你其他东西要不要拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, do you want your other stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我只要这件衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause this is all I'll need
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.63,0:21:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那堆垃圾全归你了  因为我有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can have all that junk 'cause now I've got this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有了纸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got the paper
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.97,0:21:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有我没用的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you've got my useless garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你弄不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't have it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到手了  你是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it, you're a sucker
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a sucker
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.90,0:21:37.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:37.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们该先来做什么  纸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we try first, Mr. Paper?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滑稽表演
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressions
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个人把一张纸放在鼻子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A guy with a piece of paper on his nose
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我  我一个人把一张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me, I'm a guy with a piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on his
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.91,0:21:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nose
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Helicopter
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.26,0:22:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生们  启动引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, start your engines
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm flying
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我在飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I'm flying
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm flying
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, that's right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.35,0:22:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们出发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here we go now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.81,0:22:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在飞  在飞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm flying, flying
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.58,0:22:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  更多滑稽表演
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, more impressions
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.20,0:22:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个人把一张纸狠狠扔在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A guy throwing a piece of paper on the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个人用脚踩这张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A guy stomping on the piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.92,0:22:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把所有家当都换成了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a guy who traded everything he owns for
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.84,0:22:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一张没用的纸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A worthless piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.60,0:22:52.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:52.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.18,0:22:53.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要的就是这个  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:53.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's just what I needed, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衬衣不错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice shirt, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.65,0:23:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人有防晒霜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does anybody have any sunscreen?
